{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f46b5656b7","title":"毛泽东关于释放战犯问题的意见","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"389475c0f6","index":0,"year":1975,"month":2,"day":27,"articleId":"f46b5656b7"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"5089f818cc","type":"title","text":"关于释放战犯问题的意见","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f46b5656b7"},{"id":"b9e65a57dd","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f46b5656b7"},{"id":"cfdd56195e","type":"paragraph","text":"锦州、大虎山、沈阳、长春，还有战犯为什么没有［包括］？","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f46b5656b7"},{"id":"aef54de4a6","type":"paragraph","text":"放战犯的时候要开欢送会，请他们吃顿饭，多吃点鱼、肉，每人发一百元零用钱，每人都有公民权。不要强迫改造。都放了算了，强迫人家改造也不好。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f46b5656b7"},{"id":"05504b0942","type":"paragraph","text":"土改的时候我们杀恶霸地主，不杀，老百姓怕。这些人老百姓都不知道，你杀他干什么，所以一个不杀。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f46b5656b7"},{"id":"7814f21ef8","type":"paragraph","text":"气魄太小了。十五元太少，十三人不放，也不开欢送会。有些人有能力可以做工作。年老有病的要给治病，跟我们的干部一样治。人家放下武器二十五年了。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f46b5656b7"}],"page":{"id":"3a7eb5f23c","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f46b5656b7","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}